events.name: Atlanta Hawks at New York Knicks

headlines.description: — Trae Young had 22 points and 11 assists, De'Andre Hunter and Jalen Johnson outplayed the Knicks frontcourt and the Atlanta Hawks took their surprising NBA Cup run all the way to the semifinals in Las Vegas, beating New York 108-100 on Wednesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Hawks rally for a 108-100 victory over the Knicks and a trip to the NBA Cup semifinals

events.name: Golden State Warriors at Houston Rockets

headlines.description: — Jalen Green made two free throws with 3.5 seconds left and the Houston Rockets beat the Golden State Warriors 91-90 on Wednesday night to advance to the NBA Cup semifinals in Las Vegas.
headlines.shortLinkText: Green makes late free throws, Rockets beat Warriors 91-90 to reach NBA Cup semifinals
